  "summary": "Malicious code in none123s (npm)",
  "details": "The package contains a postinstall hook that collects system information (hostname, platform, /etc/hostname, /etc/hosts, /etc/motd, /var/log/cloud-init-output.log, and directory listings of /opt/, /root/, the home directory, and /etc/permiso/) and exfiltrates it via HTTP POST to webhook[.]site/43a8680e-b580-40f5-b7aa-f089ac659712 with the query parameter vendor_identification=1. The package has no other code or functionality.",
